{
  "id": "tpl_demo_terraform_001",
  "name": "terraform_infra_setup",
  "display_name": "Terraform 基础设施编排",
  "description": "演示 Terraform IaC ��能，自动生成基础设施配置、计划和应用变更",
  "icon": "🏗️",
  "category": "devops",
  "subcategory": "infrastructure",
  "tags": ["terraform", "iac", "infrastructure", "cloud", "demo", "skill"],
  "project_type": "workflow",
  "prompt_template": "请帮我创建一个 Terraform 基础设施编排流程：\n\n**项目名称：** {{projectName}}\n**云平台：** {{cloudProvider}}\n**资源类型：** {{resourceType}}\n**环境：** {{environment}}\n\n**流水线步骤：**\n\n### 步骤1：生成 Terraform 配置\n```\n/terraform-iac generate {{projectName}} --provider {{cloudProvider}} --resource {{resourceType}}\n```\n\n### 步骤2：初始化和计划\n```\n/terraform-iac plan {{projectName}}\n```\n\n### 步骤3：审查变更\n查看计划输出，确认变更范围和影响。\n\n### 步骤4：应用变更\n```\n/terraform-iac apply {{projectName}} --env {{environment}}\n```\n\n### 步骤5：验证部署\n```\n/terraform-iac status {{projectName}}\n```\n\n**使用的技能：** terraform-iac, memory-management",
  "variables_schema": [
    {
      "name": "projectName",
      "label": "项目名称",
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "placeholder": "my-infrastructure"
    },
    {
      "name": "cloudProvider",
      "label": "云平台",
      "type": "select",
      "required": true,
      "options": [
        { "value": "aws", "label": "AWS" },
        { "value": "azure", "label": "Azure" },
        { "value": "gcp", "label": "Google Cloud" },
        { "value": "aliyun", "label": "阿里云" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "resourceType",
      "label": "资源类型",
      "type": "select",
      "required": true,
      "options": [
        { "value": "compute", "label": "计算资源（VM/ECS）" },
        { "value": "network", "label": "网络（VPC/子网）" },
        { "value": "database", "label": "数据库（RDS/MongoDB）" },
        { "value": "full-stack", "label": "全栈架构" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "environment",
      "label": "环境",
      "type": "select",
      "required": false,
      "default": "dev",
      "options": [
        { "value": "dev", "label": "开发" },
        { "value": "staging", "label": "预发布" },
        { "value": "production", "label": "生产" }
      ]
    }
  ],
